lor: rgb(64, 64, 64);">&nbsp;and&nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(128, 26, 31);"><a href="https://panama-visa.offshoreww.com/panama-reforestation-visa/" ref="nofollow">Panama Reforestation Visa</a></span><span style="color: rgb(64, 64, 64);">.</span></span></span></p><h1 style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: segoe ui, frutiger, frutiger linotype, dejavu sans, helvetica neue, arial, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 16px"><span style="color: rgb(64, 64, 64);">What is the cost of living in Panama?</span></span></span></h1><p><span style="font-family: segoe ui, frutiger, frutiger linotype, dejavu sans, helvetica neue, arial, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 20.8px"><span style="color: rgb(64, 64, 64);">The cost depends on the place you&nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(128, 26, 31);"><a href="https://panama-visa.offshoreww.com/where-do-expats-live-in-panama/" ref="nofollow">Live in Panama</a></span><span style="color: rgb(64, 64, 64);">. It is a lot less expensive to live where mostly working Panamanian people live. An average lifestyle for a couple on a budget, can cost under $1,000 and up to $3,500 to live comfortably in a prime area for expats with travel and entertainment.</span></span></span></p><p><span style="font-family: segoe ui, frutiger, frutiger linotype, dejavu sans, helvetica neue, arial, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 20.8px"><span style="color: rgb(128, 26, 31);"><a href="https://alittleadrift.com/cost-of-living/panama/#costs" target="_blank" ref="nofollow noopener noreferrer">Compare with other countries at</a></span></span></span></p><h1 style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: segoe ui, frutiger, frutiger linotype, dejavu sans, helvetica neue, arial, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 16px"><span style="color: rgb(64, 64, 64);">What’s the average salary for experienced Professionals in Panama?</span></span></span></h1><p><span style="font-family: segoe ui, frutiger, frutiger linotype, dejavu sans, helvetic